    6              / THIS HANDLER IS USED TO READ AND WRITE MAX SIZE OS/8 DEVICES OVER THE
    7              / CONSOLE SERIAL PORT.  IT MUST TALK TO THE MATCHING CSD SERVER.  THIS
    8              / MUST BE INSTALLED WITH BUILD TO WORK CORRECTLY.
